  "title": "Richly Spiced Saudi Arabian Lamb Tagine",
  "description": "A spicy and flaky Saudi Arabian dish featuring herbes-de-provence, dum, and shojin-friendly ingredients, perfect for a brunch mood. This recipe is made in a Dutch oven.",
