  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until it is softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the lamb and cook until it is browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the herbes-de-provence, dum, cumin, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add 1 cup of water to the Dutch oven and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover the Dutch oven, and simmer for 1 1/2 hours.",
    "Remove the Dutch oven from the heat and let it cool slightly.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
  ],
